## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="805a4-102">이 확장 클래스는 IIS나 WAS에서 호스트되는 서비스에만 제공됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="805a4-102">This extension is present only for services hosted in IIS or WAS.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="805a4-103">다음 예제와 같이 해당 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>에서 이 확장 클래스를 검색하여 서비스가 IIS에서 호스팅되는지 아니면 WAS에서 호스팅되는지를 확인할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="805a4-103">Services can determine whether they are hosted in IIS or WAS by retrieving this extension from their <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>, as shown in the following example.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="805a4-104">다음 예제는 서비스 호스트에서 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activation.VirtualPathExtension>을 찾아서 해당 서비스가 IIS에서 호스팅되는지 아니면 WAS에서 호스팅되는지를 나타내는 값을 반환하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="805a4-104">The following example shows how to recover the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activation.VirtualPathExtension> from the service host and return a value that it is hosted in IIS or WAS.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
bool isHosted = false;  
ServiceHostBase host = OperationContext.Current.Host;  
VirtualPathExtension vpe = host.Extentions.Find<VirtualPathExtension>();  
  
if( vpe != null )  
Console.WriteLine("The virtualPath of the hosted Service is  {0}", vpe.VirtualPath);  
```
